Bahiti is a decentralized, peer-to-peer digital currency that enables you to easily send or receive money online and a new way to make easy money investing. The purpose of the project is to launch a new coin based on Script algorithm that will present a new form of investment, available for everybody,  that is easy to obtain. Crypto coins have had a great growth in the last years, even greater than stocks and bonds and are easy to cash out.  Crypto coins are still underdeveloped and in time they will become part of our day to day lives thus increasing the price.  Even more, cryptocurrencies are not dependant on the usual industries and their fluctuations. When the fiat currency drops in price, crypto coins grow in price due to the fact that you can get more from the same coin.  Why we started creating this coin ?  In Romania, Start-Up companies that are just on the first steps on their journey do not last very much because they are not supported by the Romanian Government,  so that`s why we created this Crypto Coin to financially support both ourserves and our projects and parteners. The Pre-Sale didn`t go as expected because, as an Start-Up, we didn`t have enough money to support our marketing campaign so we decided to open the mining pool  and the wallet and to integrate Bahiti in exchanges. Our project named Bahiti will not be abandoned because Bahiti is and will be our main project and we want to evolve this project as much as possible.  What We Want To Do?                                                        We want to integrate this payment method in as many websites as possible and we want to pay our employees,servers,softwares and rents.                                                       We want to integrate our coin as balance in our future videogames or applications.                                                       We want to invest in people that are good in their domain of activity but they work in a company that pays them with almost nothing.                                                       We want to encourage students to embrace the informatics domain to evolve technology much more.  Who we are?   We are an Start-Up from Romania named S.C PentaSquad S.R.L based on IT services starting in the middle of the year 2017. We have projects based on Web Designing, Software Development, AI and now Crypto Development.  Reasons to choose Bahiti  Superior technology in privacy having zero-proof knowledge. Provides secure transactions for a stable network. Based on Proof-of-Work. It is extremely fast, you can send money to anyone in the world within seconds.
